<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DevOps Instructors</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #007BFF;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .teacher {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .teacher img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        .teacher h2 {
            color: #007BFF;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .teacher p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
        }
        .emoji {
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Meet Our DevOps Experts 🌟</h1>

        <div class="teacher">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Sir Munawar">
            <div>
                <h2>Sir Munawar 👨‍🏫</h2>
                <p>Sir Munawar is a guiding light in the world of DevOps. His wisdom and expertise help shape the future of IT professionals 🚀. A dedicated teacher who ensures every student succeeds.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="teacher">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Sir Ateeb">
            <div>
                <h2>Sir Ateeb 💻</h2>
                <p>With passion and clarity, Sir Ateeb makes even the most complex DevOps topics feel easy 💡. His enthusiasm and real-world knowledge inspire excellence in his students.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="teacher">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Sir Waqas">
            <div>
                <h2>Sir Waqas 🛠️</h2>
                <p>Sir Waqas is a master of practical insights, bridging the gap between theory and real-world applications. His hands-on teaching style empowers students to solve challenges confidently 🔧.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
